{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"罪人愿意赎取那日的刑罚，即使牺牲他的儿女、"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"他的妻子、他的弟兄，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"和那收容他的血族，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"以及大地上所有的人，但愿那能拯救自己。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"绝不然，那确是发焰的烈火，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"能揭去头皮，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"能召唤转身而逃避的人。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"他曾聚集财产加以保藏，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"人确是被造成浮躁的，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"遭遇灾殃的时候是烦恼的，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"获得财富的时候是吝啬的。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"只有礼拜的人们，不是那样，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"他们是常守拜功的；"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"他们的财产中有一个定份，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"是用于施济乞丐和贫民的；"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"他们是承认报应之日的；"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"他们是畏惧他们的主的刑罚的。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"他们的主的刑罚，确是难保不降临的。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"他们是保守贞操的，"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"除非他们对自己的妻子和奴婢，他们确是不因此而受责备的；"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"凡在这个范围之外有所要求的人，都是过份的。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"他们是尊重自己所受的信托，和自己所缔的盟约的；"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"他们是秉公作证的；"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"他们是谨守拜功的。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"这等人，是在乐园中受优待的。"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"不信道的人们，怎么注视着你们，三五成群的分列"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"在你的左右呢？"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"难道他们每个人都希望入恩泽的乐园吗？"},{"SurahNumber":70,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"绝不然！我确已用他们所知道的物质创造了他们。"}]}